The '''Govora Power Station''' is a large [[thermal power plant]] located in [[Râmnicu Vâlcea]], having 4 generation groups of 50 [[Watt#Megawatt|MW]] each having a total [[electricity]] generation capacity of 200 MW.<ref>[http://www.cet-govora.ro/cet_romana/index.php?pid=10 Structura CET Govora {{ro}}]</ref>

